# Frontend (Vercel)
# VITE_API_URL=https://your-backend.onrender.com

# ==============================================
# NOTES
# ==============================================

# 1. JWT_SECRET: Use a strong random string (min 32 characters)
#    Generate with: node -e "console.log(require('crypto').randomBytes(32).toString('hex'))"

# 2. EMAIL_PASSWORD: For Gmail, use App-Specific Password
#    - Go to Google Account → Security → 2-Step Verification → App Passwords
#    - Generate password for "Mail"
#    - Use that password here

# 3. Database: For production, use managed PostgreSQL
#    - Neon (neon.tech) - Free tier available
#    - Supabase (supabase.com) - Free tier available
#    - Railway (railway.app) - Free tier available

# 4. Never commit .env files to Git
#    - They are already in .gitignore
#    - Use environment variables in deployment platforms

# 5. Frontend URL: Must match exactly (no trailing slash)
#    - Development: http://localhost:5173
#    - Production: https://your-app.vercel.app
